{"tid":2283340,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好鍾意去donki買甜品食","createTime":"2020-11-12T13:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T02:23:23.000Z","uid":182683,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"edaa40a46927201729fde6183b1bf818860d6b3e","tid":2283340,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGVSmgL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGVSmgL.png&h=ccf11f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n次次去都掃幾盒唔同種類既甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到啲盒咁靚又忍唔住買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L85u7Xi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL85u7Xi.png&h=91eb9a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依款好香蛋味 仲有少少炭燒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口感唔係鬆軟 係比較有咬口個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但成$100盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過冇得去日本咪買下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/deWqGhv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdeWqGhv.png&h=28234c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同場加映 同依個蛋糕好夾既杏仁奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好香杏仁味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n味道：7/10<br />\n蛋糕好蛋～杏仁奶好杏仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n溝女指數：10/10 <br />\n去donki就溝到女<br />\n<br />\nIg有片有興趣可以睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=591e8caf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n<br />\n食譜就依到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=5c32350c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw</a>"},{"pid":"4dd15a09d01e232ef3b32477d9ab4f8149ab576f","tid":2283340,"uid":200408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"$100咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw樓主成日去dinky 咪好多積分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7e2f3b1755c0a2baab3b153b289486a7159b7b","tid":2283340,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"有少少想試個奶"},{"pid":"b6cdd616b7034efc7c9b74fb617909b550acce56","tid":2283340,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dd15a09d01e232ef3b32477d9ab4f8149ab576f","tid":2283340,"uid":200408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"$100咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw樓主成日去dinky 咪好多積分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"見到個盒靚就買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都幾多 我cap埋圖叫阿媽啲分比埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31ed9d718cd520f2afa222a245811af43b5074a","tid":2283340,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:28:50.000Z","msg":"朱古力蛋糕，提子蛋糕，好撚正"},{"pid":"a4e5c118c2aba713534cb7ebb487606dc1300875","tid":2283340,"uid":200408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f31ed9d718cd520f2afa222a245811af43b5074a","tid":2283340,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:28:50.000Z","msg":"朱古力蛋糕，提子蛋糕，好撚正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:30:12.000Z","msg":"有提子蛋糕咩<img src=